                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Regression introduced by &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;fff650726b LU-13642 lnet: Allow dynamic IP specification
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;/home/hornc/lustre-wc-rel/lustre/../lnet/utils/lnetctl net set --health 1000 --all
---
set:
-     net:
      errno: 3
      descr: ! &quot;Object not found&quot;
...
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The error is false meaning the command actually did what it was supposed to.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
